[src:complete-game/1954-major-league-baseball-season] Opening Day took place on April 13, featuring all sixteen teams, the first time since 1950.
[src:complete-game/1954-major-league-baseball-season] The final day of the regular season was on September 26, which saw fourteen teams play, and was the first time since 1945 that the scheduled regular season didn't end with all sixteen teams.
